Immediate action is required to identify and resolve bottlenecks. | FLOW: FLOW (Critical): Flow control is persistently active, suggesting severe resource bottlenecks or network saturation. Immediate investigation is required. | DELAY: DELAY (Degraded): Moderate DelayTime observed, suggesting intermittent wait times due to resource contention or workload imbalance. Some impact on query performance may be noticeable.
